Project Title
AI-Based Text Summarizer Using Natural Language Processing
Project Statement
Reading lengthy documents, articles, and reports can be time-consuming. The AI Text Summarizer aims to automatically generate concise and meaningful summaries from large amounts of text using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques. This helps users quickly understand the key information without reading the entire document.
Project Objectives
To develop an AI-based system that automatically summarizes text.
To reduce the length of documents while preserving important information.
To improve reading efficiency and save users' time.
To apply NLP techniques for text analysis and summarization.
To provide a simple and user-friendly interface for generating summaries
